{"id":666742,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lods","text":"Lods is a commune of 224 people (2015). It is found in the Doubs department in the Bourgogne-Franche-Comt\u00E9 region in eastern France.\nGeography.\nLods is in the Jura Mountains, about southeast of the city of Besan\u00E7on. It is in the valley of the Loue River.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Communes_of_France","surface_form":"commune","offset":10},{"uri":"Doubs","surface_form":"Doubs","offset":59},{"uri":"Departments_of_France","surface_form":"department","offset":65},{"uri":"Bourgogne-Franche-Comt%C3%A9","surface_form":"Bourgogne-Franche-Comt\u00E9","offset":83},{"uri":"Regions_of_France","surface_form":"region","offset":107},{"uri":"France","surface_form":"France","offset":125},{"uri":"Jura_Mountains","surface_form":"Jura Mountains","offset":159},{"uri":"Besan%C3%A7on","surface_form":"Besan\u00E7on","offset":206},{"uri":"Loue","surface_form":"Loue River","offset":243}]}